data.description: Spacious home with 4 bedrooms,3 full bathrooms and a large bonus room. Main level features a bedroom, full bath, living room, family room with a fireplace, and well-appointed kitchen with an island and pantry. Upper floor features primary bedroom, primary bathroom with double sinks, soaking tub and a walk-in closet, 2 additional bedrooms, hall bathroom, large bonus room and a utility room. All appliances included. Backyard with pool and tool shed. Conveniently located near the neighborhood park, this spacious home offers comfort and is perfect for those who appreciate a great living space. Welcome Home!
